      <title>格里森：红海航运风险依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/gleeson-risk-remains-around-shipping-in-red-sea-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adnoc Logistics and Services 已完成对航运和油轮运营商 Navig8 80% 股份的收购。该公司首席财务官 Nicholas Gleeson 在接受彭博社中东和非洲版 Horizo​​ns 采访时向 Christine Burke 讲述了此次收购的原因以及地缘政治目前在航运和物流中扮演的角色。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/gleeson-risk-remains-around-shipping-in-red-sea-video</guid>
